  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's one of the reasons we went away from our own town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto start in on Shovuos time on 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, someplace around then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said, I'm very bad on--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I had no idea, but in Passover time, when we were getting our new clothes-- because we got clothes twice a year, for Passover and for Rosh Hashanah-- my father had taken us to the shoemaker and all three of us were fitted with shoes, which was customary in Europe.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when the shoes came home, my father was explaining it to us, if anything happens in one point or the other and we will be separated or even just overnight-- he didn't want it to scare us-- he said, not to worry, we have all the addresses in our shoes, between the soles.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if any time, we would get into a different country or something will come up, we should not worry that we're not going to see each other anymore.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That will be something there where we could write, and he will write to the same place and they'll bring us together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the first time when I started to get scared that something is going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were able to come home in a certain time, for, like, for a half a day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was before Passover, I remember that very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came home, and I don't even think he came home after that until he came home on somehow-- somebody just brought him to the other ghetto, not even to the local place, where we were.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think Shovuos already, we, we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
